scab inspector
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:an official who inspected sheep and properties for scab infection.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:sheep inspector; stock inspector
Pronunciation:
